                                                                    Code

class Solution {
    public boolean isPerfectSquare(int num) {
        int sqrt1 = (int)Math.sqrt(num);
        return sqrt1*sqrt1 == num;
    }
}


                                                              Complexity Analysis


Time Complexity:  O(1)
Space Complexity : O(1)


                                                              Testcase Analysis


Testcase1

Input
num = 14

Output
false

Expected
false

Testcase2

Input
num = 16

Output
true

Expected
true
